, Kristina khoe b\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Sheringham. C\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd sinh em b\u00e9 trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSheringham s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 52 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 2/4. C\u1ef1u sao Man Utd v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chung m\u1ed9t con trai s\u00e1u tu\u1ed5i George. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Sheringham c\u00f3 con trai ri\u00eang Charlie v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u0169 Denise Sims. Charlie ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m hai tu\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuu sao MU chuan bi lam bo o tuoi 52  hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao MU chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0m b\u1ed1 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 52  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/Cuu-sao-MU-chuan-bi-lam-bo-o-tuoi-52--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sheringham s\u1eafp l\u00e0m b\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. \u1ea2nh: Reuters</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tay ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, Sheringham t\u1eebng \u0111i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef. Sau khi chia tay Denise v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1992, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu Katie Price v\u00e0 hoa h\u1eadu Danielle Lloyd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSheringham g\u1eb7p Kristina l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2007. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i h\u1eb9n h\u00f2, Kristina chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn chung s\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2012. Th\u00e1ng 6/2016, khi con trai George tr\u00f2n b\u1ed1n tu\u1ed5i, c\u1eb7p trai t\u00e0i g\u00e1i s\u1eafc l\u00e0m l\u1ec5 c\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Kristina k\u00e9m ch\u1ed3ng 20 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSheringham t\u1eebng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng khi ghi m\u1ed9t trong hai b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Man Utd ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bayern trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m 1999. Danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam ba danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u1ed9t Cup FA v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Cup Li\u00ean l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Sheringham \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n qua 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 51 tr\u1eadn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1966 t\u1eebng d\u1ef1 Euro 1996, 2000 v\u00e0 World Cup 1998, 2002.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"612","checkdouble":"183102"},{"date":"20:15 29/03","title":"Sao Juventus kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/7/24/sao-juventus-khong-hoi-han-vi-roi-bo-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3p