5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Arsenal m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecbu ph\u1eadn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gigi Buffon \u1edf Juventus.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Arsenal sau 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady \u1edf th\u00e0nh Turin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec3n Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Gigi Buffon v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Szczesny khong hoi han vi roi bo Arsenal den Juventus hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/24/arsenal-ban-szczesny-cho-juventus-sai-lam-lon-nhat-cua-wenger-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Arsenal. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i: \u201cV\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng t\u00f4i \u0111ang\u00a0v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Turin. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u1eady, ni\u1ec1m vui c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 chi\u1ebfm 80% quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf Juventus nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Buffon v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch suy ngh\u0129 hay nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny v\u1ed1n d\u0129 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1 g\u00ec Juventus hay m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AS Roma chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Serie A. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh Petr Cech \u1edf Arsenal, gi\u1edd anh mang tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng con s\u1ed1 23 \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Turin t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 khi Buffon tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"611","checkdouble":"183084"},{"date":"16:31 29/03","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i l\u1ea5y \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ea s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/DT-Trung-Quoc.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;backgroun