:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg/nong-u23-viet-nam-nhan-ton-that-nang-ne-truoc-ban-ket-292-178384.html\" target=\"_blank\">ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Ha Noi don tin vui truoc vong 4 V-League 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/24/clb-ha-noi-don-tin-vui-truoc-vong-4-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf&nbsp;v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai th\u00e1ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin vui v\u1edbi CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u1edf V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 28/3. S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B. B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/04. Sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 05/4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam. Sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i V\u0103n H\u1eadu, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u1edf v\u00f2ng 4<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"> V-League 2018</span> sau \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;c\u00f2i&rsquo; kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110TQG \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Jordan h\u00f4m 27/3 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-hien-chi-khung-quyet-lam-moi-san-hang-day-khong-kem-san-nha-cua-psg-168-183010.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/bau-hien-chi-khung-quyet-lam-moi-san-hang-day-khong-kem-san-nha-cua-psg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-hien-chi-khung-quyet-lam-moi-san-hang-day-khong-kem-san-nha-cua-psg-168-183010.html\">B\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n chi kh\u1ee7ng, quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m m\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a PSG</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng du t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u0103n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Bouygues, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u00