,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Unai Emery v\u1eabn l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin don PSG sa thai HLV Emery la khong co that hinh anh\" title=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n PSG sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Tin-don-PSG-sa-thai-HLV-Emery-la-khong-co-that-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>PSG b\u00e1c b\u1ecf tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i HLV\u00a0Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Coupe de la Ligue h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n 3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/nhung-hlv-co-the-thay-the-emery-dan-dat-psg-197-182878.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Unai Emery</span> v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi g\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Real Madrid lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Thomas Meunier \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1eeba qua r\u1eb1ng anh tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Di Maria c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique cho bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Unai Emery l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sai s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn HLV c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111inh: HLV c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain l\u00e0 Unai Emery. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hay l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a PSG c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/wenger-tiet-lo-cai-ten-co-the-giup-psg-thanh-cong-197-182944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/16/wenger-tiet-lo-cai-ten-co-the-giup-psg-thanh-cong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/wenger-tiet-lo-cai-ten-co-the-giup-psg-thanh-cong-197-182944.html\">Wenger ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap PSG th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 PSG, \u00f4ng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV Unai Emery.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd b\u1ecb PSG sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i uy c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. S\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eefa Cavani v\u00e0 Neymar c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt l\u00e2u cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"605","checkdouble":"183103"},{"date":"22:10 29/03","title":"Klopp khi\u1ebfn Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u00ec \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Bayern Munich","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/26/klopp-khien-liverpool-lo-sot-vo-vi-tha-thinh-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:point