=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Klopp r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jurgen Klopp r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc thay da \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ecbt Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 Anfield nh\u1eefng vinh quang r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong nay mai, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, The Kop \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp roi Liverpool ve Duc dan dat Bayern Munich hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Klopp r\u1eddi Liverpool v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/liverpool-co-the-cham-dut-su-thong-tri-cua-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Klopp r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pochettino-vs-klopp-vat-doi-sao-doi-172-171661.html\">HLV Klopp r\u1eddi Liverpool</span> l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Dortmund b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi Kopites nh\u01b0 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1ng l\u1eeda v\u00e0 lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Marc Kosicke: \u201cH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn 2022 v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec d\u1edf dang \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f4ng \u1edf Anh, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, mi\u1ec5n sao n\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Bayern Munich lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Uli Hoeness hay huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Franz Beckenbauer.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu Bayern Munich th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao HLV Klopp r\u1eddi Liverpool. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Jupp Heynckes \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng H\u00f9m X\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vao-tu-ket-champions-league-khi-jurgen-klopp-lay-lich-su-lam-diem-tua-184-181539.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/liverpool-vao-tu-ket-champions-league-khi-jurgen-klopp-lay-lich-su-lam-diem-tua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vao-tu-ket-champions-league-khi-jurgen-klopp-lay-lich-su-lam-diem-tua-184-181539.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League: Khi Jurgen Klopp l\u1ea5y l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nL\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 9 n\u0103m, Liverpool m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. V\u1eady \u