ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 29/3.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Man Utd b\u1ecb th\u00e1ch gi\u00e1 trong v\u1ee5 sao Lazio.</strong> Sergej Milinkovic-Savic hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Paul Pogba th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia c\u0169ng s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho t\u1eeb l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf kh\u00fac m\u1eafc gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lazio \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro ngang ng\u1eeda nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 mang Pogba x\u1ecbn tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Old Trafford c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bongda24h toi ngay 293 hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 293 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-293-mu-mua-pogba-moi-voi-gia-ngang-pogba-xin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 sao West Ham.</strong> C\u00f3 trong tay tam t\u1ea5u h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ea3 Premier League m\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. C\u00e1i t\u00ean HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Manuel Lanzini v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o West Ham. Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lanzini ghi ban thang duy nhat cua tran dau\" title=\"Lanzini ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/6/liverpool-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Manuel Lanzini</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd Isco.</strong> M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i v\u00e0o d\u0129 v\u00e3ng, Isco ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u00ecm ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Bernabeu sang n\u0103m nay. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0i \u0111\u0169ng qu\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda Los Blancos c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Isco nh\u01b0ng 80-90 tri\u1ec7u Euro th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng Arsenal, Chelsea hay Man City th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" title=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Real-Madrid-ban-tien-ve-Isco-trong-mua-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Isco</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng Bundesliga.</strong> \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch n\u1eb1m trong d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n khi t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Emirates hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi l\u00e0 Sven Mislintat, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Dortmund. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caglar Soyuncu, trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Freiburg. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Arsene Wenger c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kerem Demirbay c\u1ee7a Hoffenheim m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Caglar Soyuncu\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caglar Soyuncu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Gia-co-hang-thu,-Arsenal-chieu-mo-Caglar-Soyuncu--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Caglar Soyuncu</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Th\u00eam \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o tranh sao Man Utd.</strong> B\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Marouane Fellaini \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Old Trafford trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p n\u00edu k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi b\u00e9o b\u1edf t\u1eeb Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Juventus, Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Monaco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini\" title=\"Fellaini\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/16/Monaco-mua-Marouane-Fellaini-cua-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Marouane Fellaini</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Italia ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</strong> Andrea Belotti \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Torino \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd ho\u1eb7c Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u01a1n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Belotti mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Premier League ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho anh ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1edbi mong c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Andrea Belotti\" title=\"ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Andrea Belotti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/chan-sut-100-trieu-euro-ra-dieu-kien-chuyen-toi-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Andrea Belotti</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bongda24h</p>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"603","checkdouble":"183081"},{"date":"23:11 29/03","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Barca",