om:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/3.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>MU g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Ronaldo\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin Bong da 24h sang ngay 303 hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 303 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-303-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Diario Gol, Man United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Cristiano Ronaldo. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y, CR7 \u0111ang kh\u00e1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi cho anh. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Umtiti</strong><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo t\u1edd Diario Gol, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Umtiti v\u1edbi Man United. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Umtiti t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c Man United \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 9 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a khi\u1ebfn Umtiti b\u1ecb lung lay. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u1ea3 Real c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cu\u1ed7m trung v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Barca kh\u1ecfi Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tho\u00e1t th\u00e2n cho Dembele</strong><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Griezmann, Barca \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Dembele g\u1eb7p v\u00f4 v\u00e0n d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. V\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang quan s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi cho Dembele. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 Barcelona chi ra cho Dortmund \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-293-mu-mua-pogba-moi-voi-gia-ngang-pogba-xin-184-183081.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-293-mu-mua-pogba-moi-voi-gia-ngang-pogba-xin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-293-mu-mua-pogba-moi-voi-gia-ngang-pogba-xin-184-183081.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/3: MU mua &ldquo;Pogba m\u1edbi&rdquo; v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ngang Pogba x\u1ecbn</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 29/3.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Real</strong><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Real th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ceballos v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Klopp xem ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Coutinho. The Kop c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi Emre Can ra \u0111i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Roma \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Betis t\u1eeb l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Sterling</strong><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb ESPN, Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Sterling v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 an t\u00e2m ch\u00fat n\u00e0o b\u1edfi Sterling \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h (TTVN)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"601","checkdouble":"183099"},{"date":"09:03 30/03","title":"HLV Barca c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/27/hlv-barca-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-suc-khoe-cua-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-t