 color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Messi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lionel-messi-44368.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Messi</strong></span> ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo ch\u00e9o, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Argentina v\u1edbi Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u1ef1c ra th\u00ec M10 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi chan thuong, HLV Ernesto Valverde noi gi hinh anh\" title=\"Messi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Ernesto Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/hlv-barca-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-suc-khoe-cua-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lionel Messi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ee1 hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110T Argentian nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng Italia 2-0 nh\u01b0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00f2 t\u00f3t T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho th\u1ea5y M10 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNHM <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca </strong></span>\u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Messi, h\u1ecd \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Messi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/ernesto-valverde-tejedor-128.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Ernesto Valverde</strong></span>: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tham gia bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 5, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00eam v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00edt ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi tung phai tiem thuoc moi toi de chong lai chung roi loan hormone tang truong. Anh: Reuters.\" title=\"Messi t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i ti\u00eam thu\u1ed1c m\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n hormone t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/sao-tuyen-tbn-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Barca c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Messi\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMarc-Andre ter Stegen c\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Valverde chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Stegen kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang h\u01a1n Atletico Madrid 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf La Liga, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League g\u1eb7p Roma.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Ngo\u00e0i hai m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/12994-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"600","checkdouble":"183114"},{"date":"08:14 30/03","title":"Pogba b\u1ecb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU d\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/25/pogba-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-dan-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:My