 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Luke Shaw nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti t\u1eeb Barca.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti gay tranh cai khi che loi choi cua Barcelona thoi Guardiola that nham chan.\" title=\"Umtiti g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi ch\u00ea l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barcelona th\u1eddi Guardiola th\u1eadt nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/30/loi-choi-cua-barcelona-thoi-guardiola-that-nham-chan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaw \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em l\u00e0m v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U mua Umtiti t\u1eeb Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Umtiti l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford theo \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1eeb k\u1ef7 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Barcelona, HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t &quot;\u01b0ng&quot; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U</span> d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, CLB Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a M.U, Luke Shaw. Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Blaugrana s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra \u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Shaw l\u00e0m &quot;con d\u00ea t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n&quot; trong v\u1ee5 h\u1ecfi mua Umtiti. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Umtiti ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, CLB Barcelona bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Umtimi mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m v\u00e0 Man United ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y. Barca hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c n\u00e0y, g\u1ed3m Messi, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca </span>\u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 2021. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1eadu h\u0129nh cho Umtiti trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-hau-ve-canh-trai-trien-vong-ma-mu-co-the-chieu-mo-trong-he-2018-172-183087.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/5-hau-ve-canh-trai-trien-vong-ma-mu-co-the-chieu-mo-trong-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-hau-ve-canh-trai-trien-vong-ma-mu-co-the-chieu-mo-trong-he-2018-172-183087.html\">5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng m\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong h\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/96547-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3