ef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. HLV Mourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Willian v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca pha vu MU chieu mo Willian hinh anh\" title=\"Barca ph\u00e1 v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Barca-pha-vu-MU-chieu-mo-Willian-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u00fap M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf b\u1edfi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/bi-loai-khoi-champions-league-mu-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-chelsea-172-182119.html\" target=\"_blank\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span> \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u00fap M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i khi Barca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Don Balon (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea Willian v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 Willian s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Barca t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tung ra m\u1ed9t pha s\u00fat xa \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 M.U l\u1eabn Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Willian \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea</span>. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 46 ra s\u00e2n cho The Blues tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Willian \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/31417-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Willian \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-ha