;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Rhian Brewster tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-khien-liverpool-lo-sot-vo-vi-tha-thinh-bayern-munich-172-183088.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span> \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i U17 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Rhian Brewster. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111ang thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi ch\u00e0ng trai sinh th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 2000.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrewster \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U17 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017 v\u1eeba qua, Brewster \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi m\u00ecnh. Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap U17 Anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Liverpool gia han hop dong voi Rhian Brewster hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rhian Brewster h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/liverpool-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-rhian-brewster.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh Liverpool gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rhian Brewster \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-liverpool-dai-chien-gianh-sao-tre-tuyen-duc-172-183048.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span> gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rhian Brewster ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Jadon Sancho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i U17 Anh. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Sancho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Man City t\u1edbi\u00a0 Borussia Dortmund v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrewster ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c, chi ph\u00ed gia nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1edfi t\u00f2a \u00e1n. The Kop \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hlv-klopp-172-182995.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Jurgen Klopp</strong></span> c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Brewster \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u00e0 xem anh nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n khuy\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf n\u00ean tin d\u00f9ng \u201cth\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh thay v\u00ec b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn chi\u00eau binh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Brewster ra sao. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp tr\u00f2n 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Man City \u0111ang d\u00f5i theo s\u00e1t sao phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Brewster d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang d\u01b0 th\u1eeba ng\u00f4i sao. Nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb The Citizens nh\u01b0 Sancho v\u00e0 Marcus McGuane c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng Tottenham r\u1ed3i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Dortmund, RB Leipzig c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi \u201cng\u1ecdc th\u00f4\u201d c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/qbv-u20-world-cup-that-sung-van-khang-dinh-liverpool-hon-chelsea-172-183094.html\">QBV U20 World Cup th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool h\u01a1n Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-khien-liverpool-lo-sot-vo-vi-tha-thinh-bayern-munich-172-183088.html\">Klopp khi\u1ebfn Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u00ec \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-liverpool-dai-chien-gianh-sao-tre-tuyen-duc-172-183048.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-west-ham-172-183014.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao West Ham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-muon-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-cua-ac-milan-172-183013.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a AC Milan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"596","checkdouble":"183116"},{"date":"09:06 30/03","title":"Man City \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n Sterling","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/3/man-city-de-nghi-luong-khung-de-troi-chan-ster