d9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Raheem Sterling\" title=\"tien ve Raheem Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/barca-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n Sterling b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1eadu h\u0129nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 20 b\u00e0n sau 37 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p, ban b\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Man City.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c d\u00e0nh cho Sterling, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020, BL\u0110 Man xanh \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-chu-y-man-city-chua-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-raheem-sterling-172-180688.html\" target=\"_blank\">gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Sterling</span>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man City \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sterling ngay trong th\u00e1ng 4. Theo \u0111\u00f3, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang s\u1edbm \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 &quot;tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n&quot; Sterling, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad t\u00ednh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00eam 50% so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 180 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng Anh h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, Man City kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City </span>\u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Fernandinho, David Silva, Kevin de Bruyne,... \u0110i\u1ec3m chung \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i vung ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Etihad.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-anh-11-italia-tam-su-va-suc-song-moi-tu-sterling-172-183016.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/th